{"tid":437383,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 又係咁 Ielts writing 6.5","createTime":"2017-10-16T03:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T08:32:24.000Z","uid":119854,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8bd74e7e8ed9ad8839aea22514d610551d58d1df","tid":437383,"uid":119854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T03:12:06.000Z","msg":"相信好多人都考過ielts <br />\n我自己都唔例外<br />\n考過好多次<br />\n因為自己畢業果科 如果要係外國讀master要all band 7 <br />\n但係考過咁多次 每次既results都差唔多 <br />\n都係 R9 L9 S7.5  ..... W6.5 ....<br />\n考到心淡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇咩補習啊 推介 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己不嬲有温下 睇sample paper<br />\n不過睇極啲8 分啊 9 分啊 sample <br />\n覺得自己寫到 唔明點解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 癈j外國畢業 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b936560be011b1a04d5089604c4a6aa0f79c69","tid":437383,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T03:50:00.000Z","msg":"我5 6年前有準備咁左考一次writing 7左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  反而覺得speaking好難<br />\n無啊 我覺得寫得快就高分架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一part操下佢想點dsecribe啲data 第二part多數問啲野都大路 平時有記下啲examples論述時都幾易諗到point 寫快啲寫多啲就ok<br />\n同埋最緊要達多啲vocab出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025e6634ddbdfd2e0c5311788edeb214700aa955","tid":437383,"uid":21310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T04:09:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2376422cfd41a3b9afd4dc14223d5261bb398764","tid":437383,"uid":25107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T04:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>9<br />\n9<br />\n8.5<br />\n9<br />\n留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p